{"tid":703362,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)職業特工隊5 洛奇蒙牛戰記","createTime":"2018-06-15T16:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T19:28:40.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cc11813a55a5903ec17860d5e508c1c7a0080d4b","tid":703362,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:26:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=j%2BGigg9e8pTkALk91wtY6zA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=42d68349\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=j%2BGigg9e8pTkALk91wtY6zA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=d4e9ced0\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=j%2BGigg9e8pTkALk91wtY6zA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b9d2d54d\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e3/Mission_Impossible_-_Rogue_Nation_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe3%2FMission_Impossible_-_Rogue_Nation_Poster.jpg&h=7a027591&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/0c/Escape_Plan_2_Hades_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F0c%2FEscape_Plan_2_Hades_Poster.jpg&h=ba319a06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.不可能任務情報局探員伊森&middot;韓特成功攔截運往敘利亞的VX神經毒氣貨物後，認為這場成果可以證明他一直以來調查的神秘組織「辛迪加」（Syndicate）的存在。當他來到英國倫敦負責接頭的黑膠唱片行時，反而中辛迪加設下的毒氣陷阱而被抓獲，在昏倒前目睹一位神秘男子殺死和她接頭的女特務。之後，伊森遭受辛迪加幹部「拆骨師」的嚴刑拷打，但一名臥底在組織裡的軍情六處女探員伊爾莎&middot;浮士德出手相助協助他逃跑<br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述雷&middot;布瑞林為了拯救好友任樹而找來同夥德羅煞，並共同潛入一座嚴密的高科技監獄，但他們除了面對當中的各種惡煞外，還得設法破解能透過電腦而變形的監獄系統<br />\n<br />\n12 35AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=j%2BGigg9e8pTkALk91wtY6zA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=a707ce45\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=j%2BGigg9e8pTkALk91wtY6zA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=113eb4f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b9a90d6fd5e41497614b6d6628ad0224281867","tid":703362,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:29:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af43ad3efddb986801bc31c7bd77e8b70ee1113","tid":703362,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class